"content": "所以這一次，這一次我會親手割下你的頭。", "name": "沉淵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4025_aprot2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是你的預言嗎，沉淵？", "name": "頭顱"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4025_aprot2_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不會預言，這是我看到的。", "name": "沉淵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4025_aprot2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看到你死了。就算我放走你，你還是會死。", "name": "沉淵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4025_aprot2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也逃了，但我終究還是逃不過。", "name": "沉淵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4025_aprot2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你當然逃不掉。", "name": "頭顱"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沉淵，就算你藏得再好，也躲不過那些看著你的眼睛。", "name": "頭顱"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4025_aprot2_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……是誰在看著我？", "name": "沉淵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4025_aprot2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然是觀眾們。", "name": "頭顱"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4025_aprot2_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "觀眾……觀眾？", "name": "沉淵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4025_aprot2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4025_aprot2_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我演砸了，他們只會想要除掉我，為什麼還要看著我？！", "name": "沉淵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4025_aprot2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "確實，有人為你在舞台上表現出的心軟而感到憤怒，但這也是意料之中的事。", "name": "頭顱"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你我都知道，這正是藝術的魅力所在。", "name": "頭顱"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好的戲劇，好的演員，理應能夠影響他人的情緒，不是嗎？", "name": "頭顱"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4025_aprot2_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不……不是這樣，不應該是這樣！", "name": "沉淵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4025_aprot2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放過你是我自己的選擇，不是他們的安排！", "name": "沉淵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4025_aprot2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你真的能肯定……", "name": "頭顱"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼你還一直走不出這場噩夢？", "name": "頭顱"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼你明明已經逃離，卻還會反覆重現那一天？", "name": "頭顱"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼你要嘗試各種可能，要將我從那副身軀上割下，帶在身邊？", "name": "頭顱"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4025_aprot2_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……", "name": "沉淵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4025_aprot2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沉淵，你在恐懼。", "name": "頭顱"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放過我，是你唯一一次反抗。", "name": "頭顱"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從劇團的手下逃走，花光了你僅有的勇氣。", "name": "頭顱"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“血鑽”已經找上門來，你卻只能躲藏。", "name": "頭顱"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一直以來，比起害怕他們追上來，你更害怕這一切都是被操縱的。", "name": "頭顱"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不喜歡別人的目光落在你身上，因為你在擔憂，這裡根本就不存在一個“真實的自己”。", "name": "頭顱"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我說對了嗎？", "name": "頭顱"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4025_aprot2_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "沉淵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4025_aprot2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "閉上你的嘴。", "name": "沉淵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4025_aprot2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_knife", "channel": "1"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$blooddrop", "channel": "2"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你只是我夢中的惡靈，你根本不存在於此！", "name": "沉淵"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4025_aprot2_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不要叫我沉淵。", "name": "沉淵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4025_aprot2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不要叫我那個名字！", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_4025_aprot2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_knife", "channel": "1"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$blooddrop", "channel": "2"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，可憐的人，你殺不死你的恐懼，你無法讓那些疑慮閉嘴！", "name": "破碎的頭顱"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知道的，尋找自我是一種禁忌。", "name": "破碎的頭顱"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但它能成就偉大的藝術！", "name": "破碎的頭顱"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你仍然在為藝術奉獻！他們都錯誤地評價了你，你是一個傑出的演員！", "name": "破碎的頭顱"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4025_aprot2_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "閉嘴！我不是在演戲！", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_4025_aprot2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4025_aprot2_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會擺脫你，我會殺死你！", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_4025_aprot2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不會再回任何被安排好的舞台，我早就不是沉淵了，我的一切不是一場戲劇！", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_4025_aprot2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 362, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，你的小小決心。", "name": "破碎的頭顱"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，我問你。",